    "summary": {
      "value": "React to enemy spells with your invocations."
    },
    "description": "<p><strong>Requirements:</strong> you must have mastered one or more Classes among <strong>Elementalist</strong>, <strong>Entropist</strong>, <strong>Invoker</strong>, and <strong>Symbolist</strong>, and must have acquired the <strong>Invocation</strong> Skill.</p><hr /><p>After an enemy you can see hits or misses you with an offensive spell (@ICON[offensive]), if the Result of their Magic Check was an <strong>even number</strong>, you may immediately use the <strong>Invocation</strong> Skill for free (after the spell has been fully resolved) to perform an <strong>invocation</strong> you have access to against that enemy, without spending Mind Points. This invocation must not be a \"<strong>hex</strong>\", and it may target <strong>only</strong> that enemy (you cannot use the <strong>Linked Invocation</strong> Skill with it).</p>",
